      Feature Key

      • Windows Hello

        4

        Windows Hello is the password-free sign-in that gives you the fastest, most secure way to unlock your Windows devices. Using your face, fingerprint or companion device, it recognizes you apart from all others.

      • Cortana

        5

        Cortana is your truly personal digital assistant designed to help you get things done. Ready on day one to provide answers and complete basic tasks, Cortana learns over time to become more useful every day.

      • Digital pen

        6

        tool tip copy to: Take notes, navigate, draw, doodle, and edit with a digital pen.

      • Touchscreen

        Windows enables your touchscreen PC or 2-in-1 to provide a touch-first experience for those times when you want your device to feel like a tablet.

      • Security

        19

        As the most secure Windows ever built, Windows 10 delivers comprehensive protection—including anti-virus, firewall, and anti-phishing technologies—for the supported lifetime of your device.

      • S mode

        16 3 18

        With Windows 10 in S mode, you can search the web or stream movies with Microsoft Edge, choose your own cloud storage, and download your favorite apps, with the most secure Windows experience ever. And if you want a choice of browsers, you can switch out of S mode at any time.

      • Windows Mixed Reality

        13 14

        Plug your pick of headsets into a Windows Mixed Reality-ready PC, and you’re off to amazing experiences.
